metadata.name: La Taki
metadata.description:
Yacky "La Taki" Torres is a Mexican wrestler who overcame a difficult childhood to pursue her dreams. She was the first member of her family to attend college and later married after graduation. 

However, her true passion was in the ring, and after the birth of her first son, she decided to become a luchadora and began training. She quickly made a name for herself in the wrestling world, known for her fiery attitude and signature move, earning her the nickname "La Taki."
